Translation: god grant me the serenity to accept the thing i cannot change the courage to change the thing i can change and wisdom to separate the difference
Transcription: god grant me the serenity to accept the thing i cannot change the courage to change the thing i can change and wisdom to separate the difference

Translation: 神啊请赐给我雅亮从容的接受不可改变的事赐给我勇气去改变应该改变的事并赐给我智慧去分辨什么是可以改变的什么是不可以改变的
Transcription: God, give me the courage to change what needs to be changed and the wisdom to know what can be changed and what can't be changed.

Translation: 神様私に変えられないことを受け入れる落ち着きを与えてください変えられることを変える勇気を与えてくださいそして変えられるものと変えられないものを区別する知恵を与えてください
Transcription: God, give me the peace to accept the unchangeable, the courage to change the changeable, and the wisdom to distinguish the changeable from the unchangeable.

Translation: 하나님, 나에게 변할 수 없는 것을 받아들이는 온화함을 주시고, 변할 수 있는 것을 변화시키는 용기를 주시며, 변할 수 있는 것과 변할 수 없는 것을 구별하는 지혜를 주시어서
Transcription: God, give me the meekness to accept the unchangeable, the courage to change the changeable, and the wisdom to discern the changeable from the unchangeable.

Translation: พระเจ้าโปรดประทานความสงบสุขให้ข้าพเจ้ายอมรับสิ่งที่เปลี่ยนแปลงไม่ได้ มีความกล้าที่จะเปลี่ยนแปลงสิ่งที่เปลี่ยนแปลงได้ และมีปัญญาที่จะแยกแยะความแตกต่าง
Transcription: God, give me the peace to accept the unchangeable, the courage to change the changeable, and the wisdom to discern the difference.
